('2aeda534-3392-4fba-94b8-e116a5d829e2', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dresden', 'Kontaktgruppe Asyl e.V.', 'We, the members of the contact group Asylum (e. V.; short KoGA), support asylum seekers and refugees in Dresden to overcome administrative barriers and create opportunities to contact and amicable meetings. With respect, we build on the strengths and potentials of these people and provide help as spokespeople. We openly campaign against repressive stuctures and racistic prejudices and promote an open and colourful society.', '', '', '', '', '', 0, '', '', '', '', 0, NULL, '', 1, '', '556e1d2aa1087', 'en', '2015-06-02 23:16:35', '2015-06-02 23:16:35'),
